reviewText: Very happy with my purchase got exactly what I order would recommend this seller to others buyers thank you again

I purchased this volume as well as the other 3 and I highly recommend you do the same as I found that all the discs were mislabeled and arranged. (Disc 2 from Volume 3 in the Volume 1 case, etc.) Overall, I am happy; just a little stressed of making sure everything was in the right case according to the episodes.
I love the show. I miss seeing it on TV. Now I don't have to wait to see it I can see it anytime I want.
